---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy | Linda Della Industries" description="How Linda Della Industries handles website inquiry data.">
  <SiteHeader />
  <main id="main-content" class="legal-page section-shell">
    <article class="shell legal-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span>Policy</span> Effective July 16, 2026</p>
      <h1>Privacy, in plain language.</h1>
      <p class="legal-lede">This launch site collects only what is needed to answer a business inquiry. Do not submit passwords, financial records, health information, legal case details, government identifiers, or other sensitive data.</p>
      <h2>What the inquiry form collects</h2><p>Name, work email, company, optional website, the workflow description you choose to provide, and your consent to be contacted.</p>
      <h2>Why it is used</h2><p>To assess whether the requested work is a fit, respond to the inquiry, and maintain basic business correspondence. Inquiry data is not sold or used for automated decision-making.</p>
      <h2>Form delivery</h2><p>The form is delivered through FormSubmit, a third-party form-processing service. Its infrastructure receives the submission so it can be emailed to Linda Della Industries. If you prefer not to use that service, email <a href="mailto:willdoraniv@gmail.com">willdoraniv@gmail.com</a> directly.</p>
      <h2>Retention and requests</h2><p>Inquiries are kept only as long as reasonably needed for correspondence, business records, dispute prevention, or legal obligations. You may ask to access, correct, or delete your inquiry by emailing the address above. Some records may need to be retained where required by law.</p>
      <h2>Analytics and cookies</h2><p>No advertising trackers or first-party analytics are installed at launch. The hosting and form providers may process technical request data such as IP addresses and browser information as part of operating and securing their services.</p>
      <h2>Maryland notice</h2><p>The Maryland Online Data Privacy Act applies at statutory processing thresholds. This page is a transparent launch notice, not a claim that every provision applies to this independent studio or legal advice about the Act.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2><p>William Doran IV<br />Linda Della Industries<br />Baltimore, Maryland<br /><a href="mailto:willdoraniv@gmail.com">willdoraniv@gmail.com</a></p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>
